03/14/2022 News of the hour. According to the RBC agency, tonight, when the host of the Vremya program, E. Andreeva, was reading out the lead to the next story on the air, a dressed woman ran behind her with an anti-war poster in her hands and began to chant: "Stop the war! No war!". “That’s what it means to the women Instagram was turned off,” V. Zhirinovsky told our correspondent, who, despite the prohibitions of doctors, agreed to discuss this topic with him by phone.